### Back Order History API - Test Cases
### Source: ERP_Interface_backOrderHistory_07162024
### Matches EXACTLY the 4 sample requests from the specification document.
### Run with: REST Client extension in VS Code (click "Send Request" above each test)


### ============================================================
### SPEC TEST 1: Default - Get all back orders by soldTo
### Expected: List of entries for soldTo 203800 + pagination info
### ============================================================
POST http://localhost:4004/api/backorder/SearchRequest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "soldTo": "203800",
  "shipTo": "123456, 234564",
  "search": "",
  "searchBy": "",
  "fromDate": "",
  "toDate": "",
  "sort": "orderDate",
  "dir": "desc",
  "currentPage": 0,
  "pageSize": 12
}


### ============================================================
### SPEC TEST 2: Search by Order Number
### Expected: Only entries matching erpOrderNumber = 7007628
### ============================================================
POST http://localhost:4004/api/backorder/SearchRequest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "soldTo": "203800",
  "shipTo": "123456, 234564",
  "search": "7007628",
  "searchBy": "orderNumber",
  "fromDate": "",
  "toDate": "",
  "sort": "orderDate",
  "dir": "desc",
  "currentPage": 0,
  "pageSize": 12
}


### ============================================================
### SPEC TEST 3: Filter by Date Range (fromDate + toDate)
### Expected: Only entries between 2021-03-10 and 2021-12-10
### ============================================================
POST http://localhost:4004/api/backorder/SearchRequest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "soldTo": "203800",
  "shipTo": "123456, 234564",
  "search": "",
  "searchBy": "",
  "fromDate": "2021-03-10T00:00Z",
  "toDate": "2021-12-10T23:59:59Z",
  "sort": "orderDate",
  "dir": "desc",
  "currentPage": 0,
  "pageSize": 12
}


### ============================================================
### SPEC TEST 4: Filter by date AND search (orderNumber + date range)
### Expected: entries matching orderNumber 7007602 in the given date range
### ============================================================
POST http://localhost:4004/api/backorder/SearchRequest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "soldTo": "203800",
  "shipTo": "123456, 234564",
  "search": "7007602",
  "searchBy": "orderNumber",
  "fromDate": "2020-05-01T00:00:00.001+08:00",
  "toDate": "2022-05-01T00:00:00.001+08:00",
  "sort": "orderDate",
  "dir": "asc",
  "currentPage": 0,
  "pageSize": 12
}


